nodes.text: Jenson Marsh was a retired male TIE pilot that lived during the Galactic Civil War.

After his retirement from the Imperial Navy, Jenson Marsh became a freelancer pilot of the Fariso. On contract with the Imperial Research Station on Endor, he delivered important cargo to the Endor Space Station with the help of an Imperial pilot who escorted him.
